<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Music Dashboard | TETRA</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #0a0f2c;
      color: white;
    }

    header {
      background: #050a1f;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007aff;
    }

    .newsfeed {
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .post {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .post img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .post h3 {
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .post p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    }

    .timestamp {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">TETRA</div>
    <div><a href="/logout" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none;">Logout</a></div>
  </header>

  <main class="newsfeed">
    <!-- Post 1 -->
    <div class="post">
      <h3>@auroradreams released a new single: "Electric Sunrise"</h3>
      <p>Check out this synth-pop masterpiece blending retro vibes with modern beats. Now streaming everywhere.</p>
      <img src="/uploads/electric-sunrise-cover.jpg" alt="Electric Sunrise Cover" />
      <div class="timestamp">Posted 2h ago</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Post 2 -->
    <div class="post">
      <h3>@bassline_rico dropped a teaser for his upcoming EP!</h3>
      <p>Rico is coming back with a 5-track EP titled "Pulse", expect heavy bass and slick production. </p>
      <img src="/uploads/pulse-teaser.jpg" alt="Pulse Teaser" />
      <div class="timestamp">Posted 5h ago</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Post 3 -->
    <div class="post">
      <h3>@vibequeen posted behind-the-scenes from her album shoot</h3>
      <p>A raw look into the creative process. Her new album drops next month!</p>
      <img src="/uploads/vibequeen-bts.jpg" alt="Behind the scenes" />
      <div class="timestamp">Posted 1d ago</div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
